{"tid":1323450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"停止狗隻繁殖計劃","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T05:12:46.000Z","uid":189093,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"85c7547311705440807dfe0939a254c0df6ba3cd","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"致咁多位警嫂、準警嫂或者伴侶為警察的女仕，請再次三思你嘅另一半係咪合適同你過埋下半世。<br />\n<br />\n警察惡行己經去到罄竹難書嘅地步，不論男女老幼，一律照毆。係前線對無任何反抗行為嘅女性施以棍擊，你難保佢以後會唔會家暴你？單單係打女人己經唔洗再講任何嘢。<br />\n再者，佢地敢做唔敢認嘅作風實在令人不恥，明明監警會己經廢到無論，但佢地仍然收起委任証，帶哂反光物料搏記者影唔到，無恥至極。<br />\n<br />\n如果你同你警察嘅伴侶都係撐警，我祝你地好運。千萬不要分開，免得為禍人間。<br />\n<br />\n但如果你係企係良知呢邊，而你警察另一半唔係的話。請重新審視到底你係咪可以忍受一個價值觀不同的人一生一世。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我明白係要對準政權，高層。但前線人員絕對不是磨心，佢地瘋狂嘅行徑証明一切，唔好扮無辜。<br />\n<br />\n因為真係無辜果啲，通常都係無出過聲，而靜靜站係良知呢邊。"},{"pid":"661956e6210d5ebe5510612fc49bfab42848daaa","tid":1323450,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"阻人扑野 日頭又谷住 夜晚又谷住<br />\n好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bebdba33ee62dcf2f483ddb62067a355f7401c","tid":1323450,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"<em>沒有調查就沒有發言權。</em><br />\n<br />\n節錄自毛語錄<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成立獨立調查委員會</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武巴絲請入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51397dfa5c0cfa1643c37c0762ae28fb1c7ff77d","tid":1323450,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RtMcnU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RtMcnU</a>"},{"pid":"ec10b9f787b6e9205558670b053308031ba83167","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9dd72c6d02ae5062524c469ad4fba8f09386b4","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e1a05b3076ebb6f8ed7f6f57f38d99e33c8ec85","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"992770384c23241e03f60a8c75b2073f66233e22","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b68103dfda3c7c13fd1318653614acad111b4174","tid":1323450,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJ2zp3B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJ2zp3B.png&h=c95db4fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f8c8112cedf302feec94ccb62fcb9d3e4eee500","tid":1323450,"uid":40766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"通常啲女都無腦先會揀黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申睇左呢兩日警嫂留言有感"},{"pid":"cc68d708fd7715c72eb0f8cdae03aa693c458e16","tid":1323450,"uid":236193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"自己個表姊係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算"},{"pid":"d779b07e56187895405b25fd8a1a5bbd4da99fc4","tid":1323450,"uid":189093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc68d708fd7715c72eb0f8cdae03aa693c458e16","tid":1323450,"uid":236193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"自己個表姊係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"你表姊本身係警犬定佢另一半係先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}